snippet.title: Tyco R/C: Assault with a Battery - PS1 Gameplay
snippet.description:
Tyco R/C: Assault with a Battery - Gameplay

This game is nostalgic for me, I played much this game when I was about 5 or 6 years old, it's still a fun game with great graphics, good controls and an amazing soundtrack.

This is the japanese version of the game that i didn't know existed until recently, this version has some differences like the loading screen minigames that are not present in this version, and the music of the first track "frantic freeway" is different.

NOTE: Recorded in the original 4:3 aspect ratio and original game graphics (no filters, shaders etc...)

#TycoRC #PS1 #RetroGames #RetroGaming
